Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类一直在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与来自神秘远方的敌人－{\fnArial}Festum{\fn黑体}战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你死就是我亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此毫无妥协的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保存一些人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一些人牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个讲述无休止的战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存者的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:47.26,pic1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(551,425)\frz-20}欢庆毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举行了那一年的第二个「毕业」典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…今与诸位学长分别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人深感惆怅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们决不会忘记诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也请学长们一切珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勿忘岛上渡过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衷心祝愿身体健康 工作顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谨表赠别之意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭贺诸位毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有学生会长气势的告别辞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 副会长帮我斟酌的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道 你这懒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要和你分别了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空会回来转转吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「毕业」成了定局之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有些不适应 对这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽快融入大人之中反而更轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也早点确定自己的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁还能活在义务教育世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如向喜欢的人告白之类的 什么都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心存遗憾是最糟糕的 肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有留下遗憾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义务教育都没完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就进入完全不同的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是龙宫岛特有的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑和剑司一如既往的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还赌剑司赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士赌哪边赢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提剑司是13连败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去可是很要好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑和总士 他们俩小时候常在一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在一起玩是有原因的吧 相互之间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事要低头恳求身为副会长的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我「毕业」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我养着它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！带它一起走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我有事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 藏前 接下来的事拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵学长竟然先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道明天有休学典礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想说是去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他能撑着来就已经很辛苦了 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 那家伙是个懒虫也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们加油干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的 只是有些贫血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你还挺热心肠的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看你表情很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑没跟其他人一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别老等着剑司那样的人冲到面前来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要主动和别人搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说你帮了我 说这话好像不大厚道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏有你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去远见医生那边喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我这就走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间也来作检查?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚睡觉之前还好好的 今天却不能上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是遗传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵学长得的病跟妈妈一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然和妈妈没有血缘关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很羡慕羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有位真心体贴你的好母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,症状稳定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,减少止疼药的剂量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 无法再复原了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,症状也有可能完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那个选拔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚 情况一定不会悲观的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 听说可以自愿参加 松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最害怕一事无成就结束了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母亲去世已经两年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独立生活有困难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛这么小 总有人帮我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 我也不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间 不回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢马上就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 有个好朋友真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的好朋友一半以上都「毕业」了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵学长真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持上学 还当学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在我休假时 大家擅自决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自决定?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 一上学就突然多了个头衔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然这样 不觉得讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像硬塞给你似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家没有忘记我 很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为我准备了容身之处 我应该报恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算去学校 恐怕也没有容身之处了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍惜陪在你身边的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校长 真壁叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 生驹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我马上去沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 只是来打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走了 生驹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心养病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 今天上午又举行「毕业」典礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放暑假之前 举行好几次「毕业」典礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是个荒僻的小岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸小时候的毕业典礼也是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我「毕业」后会去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门重复发出反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预计700小时之内将得到明确应答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不能迎击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上的核正在形成人格 若此时和敌人接触
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整座岛都被夺取的可能性太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是只能将防御系统降低到极限吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们直接跟生驹谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点将全部{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}相关兵器严密封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为将被敌人夺取后的打击降到最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能主动封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 仅此实在不能算是万全之策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此生驹所提出回避危机的计划 即是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fn黑体}计划?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若要实施 {\fnArial}TSX{\fn黑体}的投入是大前提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 难道要让孩子们参与吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要掌控这个岛的人们共同决断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（暑假）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要打赢你 别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天要和朋友出去一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友约我去海边玩 很快就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒让我想起这岛虽小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候却也不愁找不到地方玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你约我来的 自己却不下去游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:14:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你的泳姿 就失去信心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 你去看过远见医生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 只是有些不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微能明白这样的人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直和爸爸生活在一起 习惯照顾人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体也晒暖了 去游一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想过让别人照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果伤了你的心 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很开心 许久未曾这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至能稍微抛开爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Al…vis…{\fn黑体}必须…得去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去{\fnArial}Alvis…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士同学 令尊常去看我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 说是在公事上听取一些建议
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fn黑体}吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Plan…L
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fn黑体}计划?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner…Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis{\fn黑体}是为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吗 你在那里吗 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,识别限制编码确认为第三级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}TSX
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}TS…X
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你「毕业」 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的声音一直在我脑海里回响
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催眠学习({\fnArial}Memorizing{\fn黑体})的知识\N是作为声音来被认知的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到的是妈妈的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催眠学习?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小开始就被无意识灌输的各种知识
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现今的世界形势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在于岛内部的{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及与敌人战斗的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fn黑体}的人就算「毕业」了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦知道 就无法回到平常的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要选择和大人们一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚为什么没有离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲所设立的拯救岛的L计划启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对父亲的事情一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲一定想让我参加这个计划
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会念着{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 你还什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就一直都明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没跟你出去 爸爸就不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:39.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,正冈前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的指令书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何也要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下终于可以报答给我容身之处的人们了
Comment: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要选择和父亲相同的道路吗
Comment: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您成全
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 选拔成员聚齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够自主催眠学习
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协成率形成度高的最适格者们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:23:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是今天起负责各位训练的日野惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想退出作战的人可随时向我提出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始说明{\fnArial}L{\fn黑体}计划的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是{\fnArial}Alvis{\fn黑体}的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在敌人正逐渐察觉此岛的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fn黑体}计划正是为了避免之
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fn黑体}即指{\fnArial}Alvis{\fn黑体}的左翼 {\fnArial}L{\fn黑体}区域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.64,0:23:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其从岛上分离开 成为{\fnArial}L Boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fn黑体}能够在超越敌人探知能力的深海中前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到岛的防御圈外上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引敌人 按既定航线继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为期两个月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让其误以为{\fnArial}L Boat{\fn黑体}就是龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须持续迎击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.13,0:23:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘{\fnArial}L Boat{\fn黑体}是自动驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己身在何处也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这将是极其苛刻的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想退出的人请提出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.64,0:24:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么立即开始训练
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}的第一大特征 即无需操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.45,0:24:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要遵从催眠学习获得的知识 和{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}一体化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受精神的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.49,0:24:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是训练用的虚拟现实
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.17,0:24:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.73,0:24:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.52,0:24:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.21,0:24:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能跑 这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.05,0:24:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸毫无困难
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.67,0:24:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 这不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.51,0:24:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.01,0:24:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二大特征 即各机内置系统间的交叉({\fnArial}Crossing{\fn黑体})
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.47,0:24:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共享思考 防止被敌人读取
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.80,0:25:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要接受同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.56,0:25:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.51,0:25:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.12,0:25:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.01,0:25:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 请换其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.90,0:25:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了取得平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.84,0:25:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是他 你马上就能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.98,0:25:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.97,0:25:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.01,0:25:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未 你害怕了?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.49,0:25:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是僚的感觉?你在享受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.29,0:25:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘上这个 我也能游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.68,0:25:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制时间到 请离开驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.95,0:25:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}的第三大特征
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.10,0:25:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即驾驶员会被同化现象所侵扰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.28,0:25:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐次数越多 肉体越容易发生异常
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.98,0:25:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最坏情况下可能危及生命
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.74,0:25:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退出吧 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.40,0:26:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干不了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.39,0:26:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了爸爸一定要让计划成功
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.88,0:26:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是一开始就不想活着回去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.16,0:26:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如退出算了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.44,0:26:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选拔成员共8人 无人退出
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.29,0:26:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}共4架 每架由两人交替驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.27,0:26:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次战斗时间15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.37,0:26:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人交替 各战斗450秒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.90,0:26:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断重复的战斗训练 以及敌人的确认
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.76,0:26:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硅状生命体－{\fnArial}Festum {\fn黑体}即敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.61,0:26:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有统一的思考 能适应任何环境
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.96,0:26:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但未曾在海中发现过
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.77,0:26:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据推测是其若与海中结晶物同化
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.78,0:26:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会成为不规则块状物
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.94,0:26:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是「毕业」的准备工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.84,0:26:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而对我来说 还有一项重要的准备工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.03,0:27:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 普库 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.42,0:27:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我给的 它从不吃任何食物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.98,0:27:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定察觉到会被丢下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.17,0:27:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能带狗一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.21,0:27:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为饲主 要负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.39,0:27:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条狗是从前妈妈带回来 让我当成朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.64,0:27:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法去上学时
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.46,0:27:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有它在身边 我就不会感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.59,0:27:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.39,0:27:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知有毒还去吃的对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.43,0:27:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.93,0:28:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.17,0:28:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖等着学长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.40,0:28:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为奖励 学长们的慰问品分你一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.56,0:28:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的新型{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.65,0:28:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.63,0:28:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个月后计划完毕之前 应该赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.86,0:28:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们没事 就能来迎接我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.38,0:28:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.15,0:28:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵学长 它好像肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.00,0:28:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.72,0:28:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这是随身物品 可能有些沉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.24,0:28:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.04,0:28:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.99,0:28:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我会把它当成学长好好珍视
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.86,0:28:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.87,0:28:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是做好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.96,0:28:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.14,0:28:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 完成最后一项准备时
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.56,0:28:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何想起了祐未的话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.64,0:29:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就觉得回不去的人 应该退出
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.15,0:29:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.40,0:29:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 多半祐未是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.99,0:29:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伪装镜面 维持{\fnArial}ROM{\fn黑体}模式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.06,0:29:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接续区域 全部隔离壁以紧急模式封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.00,0:29:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全隔离壁封锁确认
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.72,0:29:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开启注水阀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.48,0:29:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接续区域 确认注水
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.94,0:29:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fn黑体}舰桥呼叫{\fnArial}CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.18,0:29:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程序链接无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.99,0:29:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注水完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.12,0:29:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat {\fn黑体}出发准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.08,0:29:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fn黑体}区域分离准备 全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.82,0:29:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分离
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.21,0:29:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fn黑体}控制程序开始运行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.03,0:29:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驶向波盾圈外
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.03,0:29:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个月后再会
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.75,0:29:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝他们好运
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.08,0:29:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二步骤启动 作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.21,0:29:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.84,0:30:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离计划结束的时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.98,0:30:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9月2号 {\fnArial}L{\fn黑体}计划启动
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.26,0:30:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fn黑体}即{\fnArial}Left {\fn黑体}左边
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.65,0:30:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也含有离去的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.67,0:30:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如这个词所说 我们离开了岛
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.42,0:30:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发后第3天 我们的小岛上浮了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.07,0:30:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天起 这里就是龙宫岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.62,0:30:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人实体化 是{\fnArial}Sphinx {\fn黑体}型
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.85,0:30:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以普通武器牵制 {\fnArial}Fafner {\fn黑体}准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.67,0:30:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}能量传输线连接
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.06,0:30:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}7至8号
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.53,0:30:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Brunhild{\fn黑体}系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.97,0:30:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}数据线确认
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}搭乘输入优先
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.98,0:30:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}速度控制
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.11,0:30:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}负极数据输入中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.36,0:30:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}误差修正
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.14,0:30:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}传感器开放
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.14,0:30:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}各机正常
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.47,0:30:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}封锁解除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.99,0:30:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Niebelungen{\fn黑体}系统开启确认
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.75,0:30:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fn黑体}系统接续完成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.09,0:30:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}接续杆连接
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.28,0:30:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}舱门开启
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.63,0:30:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}启动升降架接续
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.39,0:30:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}上升
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.49,0:31:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}潮流数据 环境数据及气象数据输入完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.45,0:31:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到的敌人 超乎想象的美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.04,0:31:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未 打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.08,0:31:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.99,0:32:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 打倒敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.63,0:32:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次打倒敌人 大家深受鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.25,0:32:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试图用兴奋压抑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.81,0:32:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有归路了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.09,0:33:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我想象的小
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.89,0:33:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有内置{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fn黑体}系统
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.68,0:33:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.17,0:33:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.82,0:33:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.17,0:33:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Markeins {\fn黑体}终止启动
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.42,0:33:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20}{\fnArial}eins:{\fn黑体}德语「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.10,0:33:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然对与{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}一体化来说 是致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.86,0:33:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次 请让我再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.45,0:33:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行 动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.55,0:33:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.93,0:34:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员丧失意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.19,0:34:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3号机的驾驶员来这边 交换
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.28,0:34:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.37,0:34:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天一次 敌人不断来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.51,0:34:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后有人牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.67,0:34:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第6次战斗时 那件事发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.27,0:34:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是乘坐{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.24,0:34:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员的肉体越会结晶化
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.78,0:34:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.67,0:34:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第8次战斗时 又有一人倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.60,0:34:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.12,0:35:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是敌人 而是本应是武器的{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.82,0:35:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为减少驾驶员的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.63,0:35:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该把战斗时间从15分钟缩短为10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.16,0:35:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样出击次数就会增大
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.72,0:35:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击时 牵制敌人的弹药不足
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.38,0:35:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相反需要增加战斗时间
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.76,0:35:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.19,0:35:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生驹
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.39,0:35:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从父亲口中听说过这个计划的内容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.81,0:35:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.10,0:35:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划结束时的逃生方法是什么 连我也未被告知
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.96,0:35:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便没有逃生方法 我也早有心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.09,0:35:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父…父亲他 绝不会把我们当成牺牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.96,0:35:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未的父亲并不笨
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.29,0:35:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能提出这么快就无法战斗的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.72,0:35:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该缩短战斗时间到10分钟 减少驾驶员的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.98,0:36:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与根据现状的判断相比 你更相信计划立案者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.17,0:36:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未的父亲自己也打算参加
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.35,0:36:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为他想活着回岛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.59,0:36:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说重病缠身时日无多的人还打算生还吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.24,0:36:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.26,0:36:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.92,0:36:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知从何时起 我就变得如此相信
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.86,0:36:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.43,0:36:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得 如果自己病情严重恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.47,0:36:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会比现在更想活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.96,0:36:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人在放哨?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.10,0:36:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.47,0:36:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.71,0:36:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.22,0:36:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.02,0:36:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.45,0:36:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太担心的话 你又要发火了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.14,0:36:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候被人提起自己的身体 有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.98,0:36:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天谢谢你 替我父亲辩护
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.35,0:36:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是辩护
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.39,0:37:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是…对不起 你父亲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.52,0:37:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为无法活着回去也无所谓的 是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.97,0:37:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 你一直想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.14,0:37:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你和爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.55,0:37:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是唯有你 我不想失去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.43,0:37:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快到会议室来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.32,0:37:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.49,0:37:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封闭的区域自动开启了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.06,0:37:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是给我们的补给
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.05,0:37:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.63,0:37:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人会读取我们的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.13,0:37:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判断武器的能力而进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.92,0:37:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要骗过敌人先得骗过自己 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.57,0:37:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.57,0:37:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在一定时期后 就会提供一些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.71,0:38:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而最后打开的…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.75,0:38:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是逃生的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.70,0:38:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 勿庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.22,0:38:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸果然了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.70,0:38:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要的一定是生存之地 而不是葬身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.62,0:38:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.92,0:38:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员另选其他人担任
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.57,0:38:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来操纵{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fn黑体}系统 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.71,0:38:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您叫我不亲临阵前 反而把同伴送去战场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.71,0:38:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这比较适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.22,0:38:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲认为这次计划能有多少人生还
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.87,0:38:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生驹提岀的生存率极低
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.92,0:38:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但您依然批准了计划
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.25,0:38:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要我做同样的事 为了保护岛而付出牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.98,0:38:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生驹想尽力生存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.09,0:39:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我批准了计划
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.66,0:39:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坚信他们能够全部生还
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.47,0:39:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在残酷的境遇中挣扎求生者的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.84,0:39:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能够背负吗 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.48,0:39:22.59,pic2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(473,201)}活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.49,0:39:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗越来越激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.76,0:39:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.81,0:40:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.17,0:40:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.23,0:40:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅有的4架{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}中 有一架丧失了机能
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.59,0:40:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员的数量再次减少
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.78,0:40:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚能战斗的人身上 也出现了同化现象的早期症状
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.84,0:40:32.61,pic3,NTP,0,0,0,,（希望早日结束）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.93,0:40:33.61,pic4,NTP,0,0,0,,（快点！快点！快点！我想回家！）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.79,0:40:34.51,pic5,NTP,0,0,0,,（爸爸 妈妈）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.65,0:40:35.28,pic6,NTP,0,0,0,,（我们在这里）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.90,0:40:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 终于驾驶员中也开始出现牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.70,0:40:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸弘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.63,0:41:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是同化现象的末期症状
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.88,0:41:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴们 一个接一个 在我们眼前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.59,0:41:20.05,pic7,NTP,0,0,0,,（反正大家最后都要死）
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.22,0:41:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 为什么写这个
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.98,0:41:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.00,0:41:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.92,0:41:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再逼他了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.99,0:41:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人的心中都充满了恐惧 愤怒和悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.73,0:41:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩下两周
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.48,0:41:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我们再度失去了{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}和驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.62,0:42:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化现象的早期症状吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.87,0:42:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.11,0:42:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏这个 才不会被其他人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.85,0:42:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在第三次启动时成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.18,0:42:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样身体就出现异变 真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.13,0:42:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵学长他们还要更加辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.55,0:42:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一派和平
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.32,0:42:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想把学长们的事告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.36,0:42:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会让学长们的战斗变得毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.28,0:42:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人做出牺牲 却只有我们待在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.51,0:42:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样正确吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.70,0:42:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能祈求这是正确的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.59,0:42:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说皆城已经决定操纵系统了?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.43,0:42:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.81,0:42:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸存下来的有两架{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.95,0:42:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3名驾驶员和8位成人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.76,0:43:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.01,0:43:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里竟然有通道
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.20,0:43:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是逃生方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.56,0:43:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.49,0:43:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.43,0:43:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.36,0:43:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗 那艘潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.19,0:43:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够搭乘40人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.11,0:43:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸认为所有人都能生还
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.26,0:43:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.74,0:43:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经活到现在了 一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.26,0:43:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}第9至第17区域注水开始
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.98,0:43:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}第1第2第3隔离壁开启
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.41,0:43:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}逃生程序确认
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.12,0:43:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fn黑体}启动
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.39,0:43:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想与{\fnArial}Festum{\fn黑体}同归于尽 销毁这个岛吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.21,0:43:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.67,0:43:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.96,0:44:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fn黑体}释放还有5
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.99,0:44:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.95,0:44:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.90,0:44:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.77,0:44:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.64,0:44:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防御圈内有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.55,0:44:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是潜水艇和{\fnArial}Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.40,0:44:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备出击 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.61,0:44:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner·Markzwei {\fn黑体}出击
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.15,0:44:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20}{\fnArial}zwei:{\fn黑体}德语「2」
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.13,0:44:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中间正面出现{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.02,0:44:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短鱼雷及导弹战准备
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.09,0:44:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,252度也出现敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.54,0:44:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.53,0:45:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.34,0:45:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后方约20公里处
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.50,0:45:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.49,0:45:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们几时能下水了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.53,0:45:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜水艇消失
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.93,0:45:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.72,0:45:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛应该在这个方向 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.23,0:45:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.21,0:45:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能过去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.32,0:45:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经知道龙宫岛在这前面了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.22,0:45:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.88,0:45:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能百分之百确定 就不能这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.87,0:45:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.24,0:45:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回去 回岛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.62,0:45:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况已经变了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.08,0:45:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能让大家的战斗失去意义
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.77,0:45:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 在有人来迎接我们之前
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.82,0:45:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Titan-model{\fn黑体}开始移动
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.19,0:45:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远离岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.24,0:46:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 停住{\fnArial}Markzwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.60,0:46:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能发生了最坏的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.21,0:46:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.70,0:46:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让整座岛置身险境 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.60,0:46:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Markzwei {\fn黑体}停止前进
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.74,0:46:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 不去接学长他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.37,0:46:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待机 {\fnArial}Markzwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.99,0:46:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况变了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.20,0:46:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 不是要去接学长他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.17,0:46:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.69,0:46:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待机！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.21,0:46:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我绝不认同
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.66,0:46:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定{\fnArial}Markzwei{\fn黑体}的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.46,0:46:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你让我去 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.36,0:46:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城 听得见吧 为什么不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.93,0:46:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.07,0:46:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.46,0:46:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}CDC {\fn黑体}那边是有着实战经验的机体和驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.83,0:46:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能回收那些数据
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.68,0:47:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的战力将大幅提升
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.35,0:47:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也更能抵抗敌人的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.24,0:47:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.27,0:47:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得与敌人战斗力量的绝好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.27,0:47:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您打算眼睁睁地错过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.36,0:47:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}是做什么用的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.58,0:47:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.82,0:47:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不能让{\fnArial}Fafner{\fn黑体}离开防御圈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.71,0:47:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.51,0:47:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Markzwei {\fn黑体}重整机体
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.17,0:47:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后全力追击
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.13,0:47:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.78,0:47:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计测目标周边所有振动
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.11,0:47:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.74,0:47:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就能得到答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.29,0:47:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潮流的数据收集到了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.50,0:47:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这里运气好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.54,0:47:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少残骸能回到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.41,0:47:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.77,0:47:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.29,0:48:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 制止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.26,0:48:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.41,0:48:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.20,0:48:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.64,0:48:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我一直喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.99,0:48:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能 从很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.94,0:48:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是不是喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.89,0:48:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时 已经超越了那种感情
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.16,0:48:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.22,0:48:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.33,0:48:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上的人们会知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.89,0:48:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.15,0:48:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸会称赞我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.30,0:49:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪?下在海底?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.76,0:49:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.76,0:49:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20}注:海底浮游生物组成的絮状物，看起来像雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.67,0:49:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在称赞我们呢 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.73,0:49:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.40,0:49:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在陪在我身边的是你 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.43,0:49:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.04,0:49:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.89,0:49:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.33,0:49:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像还有更多更深的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.46,0:49:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你陪在身边 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.40,0:50:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.86,0:50:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.56,0:50:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了吗 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.09,0:50:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我们的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.79,0:50:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷有人能听到这些
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.42,0:50:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你们以前从未到过海中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.56,0:50:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由于无法代谢而结晶化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.54,0:51:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代谢…就是使身体重生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.28,0:51:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也掌握了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.19,0:51:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 才拥有了生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.23,0:51:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fenrir{\fn黑体}释放
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.40,0:51:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认信源地
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.12,0:51:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判断为海底有人启动了{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.97,0:51:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.77,0:51:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心机体被敌人同化
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.62,0:51:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这说明海底也存在{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.95,0:51:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是给我们的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.17,0:51:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Markzwei 返航
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.77,0:51:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里已经 没有任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.05,0:52:05.43,pic8,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,276)\fad(2000,2000)\fscx150}四\N个\N月\N后
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.10,0:52:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是第一波盾的潮流感应器探查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.34,0:52:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着珍贵的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.09,0:52:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.18,0:52:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 分析了潮流后才启动的{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.53,0:52:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是保持镇静直到最后的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.05,0:52:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁驾驶的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.56,0:52:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据调查 似乎只留下了音频记录
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.88,0:52:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 普库 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.42,0:52:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.47,0:52:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我们的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.50,0:53:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷有人能听到这些
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.39,0:53:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普库
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.30,0:53:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 待在这里的是将陵学长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.94,0:53:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是陪伴祐未学姐直到最后的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.94,0:54:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起 一定是去了将陵学长身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.57,0:54:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回去了 想把它送回龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.37,0:54:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门的反应显示着征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.97,0:54:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预计很快将轮到{\fnArial}Alvis{\fn黑体}迎击了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.03,0:54:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平仅仅维持了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.50,0:54:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将陵学长他们的战斗 只有这点意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.97,0:54:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直享受着别人赢来并让给的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.87,0:54:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便那和平只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.16,0:54:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会感谢其价值
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.48,0:54:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.52,0:54:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待与你并肩作战的时刻到来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.13,0:55:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我们继承了和平与战争
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.02,0:55:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想要活下去的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.38,0:55:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及在前线战斗者的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.62,0:55:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能否全部承受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.08,0:55:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不断重复问着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.11,0:55:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案 就在今后的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.59,0:55:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.69,0:52:28.22,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,どれくらい時間があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.00,0:52:32.88,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心は繋がるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.12,0:52:39.66,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,どこか寂しげな笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.02,0:52:44.12,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,癒せたらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.74,0:52:52.15,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,近すぎて気づけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.96,0:52:57.31,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,一番大事な人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.92,0:53:03.69,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,傍に居てくれるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.00,0:53:09.36,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,幸せを感じられる
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.56,0:53:12.44,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しみの夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.51,0:53:15.44,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,喜びの朝も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.51,0:53:21.47,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしを見守ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.98,0:53:27.63,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ一言「ありがとう」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.97,0:53:32.96,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,伝えられないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.45,0:53:36.36,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.49,0:53:39.32,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.53,0:53:45.24,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,今あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.04,0:53:51.94,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心がほどけてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.18,0:54:01.14,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,温かい安らぎに抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.69,0:54:16.15,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,静けさにふと窓の外
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.01,0:54:20.92,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,雪が舞い降りている
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.01,0:54:27.30,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,真白に染まる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.06,0:54:33.28,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたの音に寄り添う
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.56,0:54:36.36,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.50,0:54:39.43,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.60,0:54:44.95,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.04,0:54:51.91,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心がほどけてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.30,0:55:02.47,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,温かい安らぎに抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.69,0:52:28.22,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,要经过多少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.00,0:52:32.88,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,心才能相映
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.12,0:52:39.66,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,些许寂寞的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.02,0:52:44.12,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,多想将其治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.74,0:52:52.15,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,太过靠近而未曾察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.96,0:52:57.31,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.92,0:53:03.69,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,只是陪在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.00,0:53:09.36,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.56,0:53:12.44,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤的夜晚
